     <para>
      避免在 <application>initdb</application> 期间启用
      <varname>track_commit_timestamp</varname> 时的断言失败
      （Hayato Kuroda、Andy Fan）
      <ulink url="&commit_baseurl;ae20c105f">&sect;</ulink>
     </para>
    </listitem>

    <listitem>
<!--
Author: Fujii Masao <fujii@postgresql.org>
Branch: master Release: REL_18_BR [0bd762e81] 2025-05-21 11:55:14 +0900
